messages.message:
Cross-posting! We're excited to release a new version of the AI Hub results API that is meant to deliver more comprehensive run results (in a much easier way!) to our customers. Users can now pass as parameters into run results API:
• include_review_results: When set to true, details such as review status and edits at the run or document level and the extracted field level are included.
• include_confidence_scores: When set to true, classification confidence scores at the run or document level and extraction confidence scores at the extracted field level are included
• include_validation_results: When set to true, validation results at the run or document level and extracted field level are included.
• include_source_info: When set to true, source details such as the image path of the generated image are included in the results. 
Can't wait for you all to try it out and give feedback!
